    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s been well-loved and kept in wonderful shape, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! It runs super smoothly and is perfect for anyone looking for a solid, dependable ride that still looks sharp on the road. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014feel free to reach out and come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
